It’s rare to find a teammate who checks every box. There are not many people who are top tier in every aspect of the game and as selfless as one could possibly be. Tyler Harmon can play every position on the field exceptionally. He is an excellent communicator, gunfighter, and clutch performer. He always puts the team first. He faces adversity head on and always looks for a solution rather than shift blame. There is no player more energetic and electrifying than Tyler Harmon. He doesn’t get tired or dejected. He is positive and uplifting all day towards everybody. His passion for the sport, the culture, and the community are unmatched. Someone who embodies faith, perseverance, hard work, competitiveness, commitment, altruism, and kindness is an easy description of one of the best people I know. I am proud to add this throwback to my personal Hall Of Fame Collection.
